Class Properties

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Hashtable<Object,Object>
      • java.util.Properties
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PilotProps

    public class Properties
extends Hashtable<Object,Object>
    Properties class, used to store properties using a key, and retrieving properties with a key. String for both. Integrates well with File for saving to file system.
